databcrd

The goal of {databcrd} is to make the data shared by the Central Bank of the Dominican Republic (DR) accessible to R users via an R packages. With the the functions contained in this package, downloading, cleaning and importing data about DR economy will be simple.

Installation

You can install the development version of databcrd like so:

remotes::install_github("johan-rosa/databcrd")
